text: Ouran High School Host Club is a manga created by Bisco Hatori. == Plot == The manga and anime are centered around Haruhi Fujioka, who is a girl mistaken for a boy, and the Host Club which she belongs to. Haruhi is a commoner, and quite poor, whereas the other Host Club members are very rich. ==References== Category:2011 Japanese television series debuts Category:Bones (studio) Category:Cross-dressing in video games
